{
  "QuestID": 315509,
  "QuestText": {
    "QuestInfo": [
      {
        "Language": "JPN",
        "Name": "\u6C37\u70B9\u4E0B\u306E\u652F\u914D\u8005",
        "Client": "\u9003\u3052\u5E30\u3063\u3066\u304D\u305F\u6751\u4EBA",
        "Description": "\u4FFA\u306F\u898B\u305F\u3002\u78BA\u304B\u306B\u898B\u305F\u3093\u3060\u3002\r\n\u8996\u754C\u306E\u9589\u3056\u3055\u308C\u305F\u5439\u96EA\u306E\u4E2D\u5FC3\u3001\r\n\u7A7A\u3092\u821E\u3046\u9ED2\u3044\u7FFC\u3092\uFF01\u2026\u3044\u3044\u304B\u3001\r\n\u3042\u308C\u306F\u4EBA\u9593\u306B\u52DD\u3066\u308B\u76F8\u624B\u3058\u3083\r\n\u306A\u3044\u3002\u7D76\u5BFE\u306B\u884C\u3063\u3061\u3083\u30C0\u30E1\u3060\uFF01 ",
        "Target": "\u30AF\u30B7\u30E3\u30EB\u30C0\u30AA\u30E9\uFF11\u4F53\u306E\u8A0E\u4F10",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Frozen Dictator",
        "Client": "Fleeing Villager",
        "Description": "I saw it! I saw it! In the\r\nmiddle of a blinding snow\r\nstorm, there it was; dark\r\nblack wings were dancing in\r\nthe sky... No mere human\r\ncould stand up to it! Don\u0027t\r\neven think of hunting it!",
        "Target": "Slay a Kushala Daora",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Le dictateur glacial",
        "Client": "Villageois en fuite",
        "Description": "Je l\u0027ai vu ! Je le sais !\r\nDes ailes noires dans la\r\nneige... Un bon conseil,\r\nne vous approchez pas\r\nde cette cr\u00E9ature !",
        "Target": "Tuer un Kushala Daora",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Il dittatore ghiacciato",
        "Client": "Paesano in fuga",
        "Description": "L\u0027ho visto! Non ho alcun dubbio!\r\nDue ali nere in un turbine di\r\nneve! Credimi, quel mostro\r\n\u00E8 inavvicinabile!",
        "Target": "Uccidi un Kushala Daora",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Der gefrorene Diktator",
        "Client": "Fliehender D\u00F6rfler",
        "Description": "Ich habe sie gesehen! Mitten in\r\neinem blendenden Schneesturm!\r\nDa waren sie, dunkle schwarze\r\nSchwingen tanzten am Himmel...\r\nKein normaler Mensch k\u00F6nnte\r\nihnen widerstehen! Denk nicht\r\nauch nur daran, sie zu jagen!",
        "Target": "Erlege einen Kushala Daora.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "El dictador glacial",
        "Client": "Aldeano huidizo",
        "Description": "\u00A1Lo he visto! \u00A1Lo he visto!\r\nAll\u00ED estaba, en mitad de una\r\ntormenta de nieve: unas alas\r\nnegras bailando en el cielo...\r\n\u00A1Ning\u00FAn humano podr\u00EDa\r\njam\u00E1s enfrentarse a \u00E9l!\r\n\u00A1Y ni pienses en cazarlo!",
        "Target": "Abate un Kushala Daora",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041B\u0435\u0434\u044F\u043D\u043E\u0439 \u0434\u0438\u043A\u0442\u0430\u0442\u043E\u0440",
        "Client": "\u0411\u0435\u0433\u0443\u0449\u0438\u0439 \u0436\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043B\u044C",
        "Description": "\u042F \u0432\u0438\u0434\u0435\u043B \u0438\u0445! \u0412\u0438\u0434\u0435\u043B! \u041F\u0430\u0440\u0430 \u0447\u0435\u0440\u043D\u044B\u0445\r\n\u043A\u0440\u044B\u043B\u044C\u0435\u0432 \u0432 \u0441\u043D\u0435\u0436\u043D\u043E\u0439 \u0431\u0443\u0440\u0435...\r\n\u041F\u043E\u0441\u043B\u0443\u0448\u0430\u0439 \u043C\u043E\u0435\u0433\u043E \u0441\u043E\u0432\u0435\u0442\u0430 \u0438\r\n\u043D\u0435 \u043F\u043E\u0434\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438 \u0442\u0443\u0434\u0430 \u0431\u043B\u0438\u0437\u043A\u043E!",
        "Target": "\u0423\u0431\u0438\u0442\u044C \u041A\u0443\u0448\u0430\u043B\u0443 \u0414\u0430\u043E\u0440\u0443",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Zamarzni\u0119ty dyktator",
        "Client": "Uciekaj\u0105cy mieszkaniec",
        "Description": "Widzia\u0142em to! Na pewno!\r\nPara czarnych skrzyde\u0142 w\r\n\u015Bnie\u017Cycy... Radz\u0119 ci, nie\r\nzbli\u017Caj si\u0119 do tego!",
        "Target": "Zabij Kushal\u0119 Daor\u0119",
        "Fail": "Nagroda r\u00F3wna 0 lub\r\nkoniec czasu"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POR",
        "Name": "Ditador Congelado",
        "Client": "Alde\u00E3o Fugitivo",
        "Description": "Eu vi! Eu sei que vi! Um par\r\nde asas pretas em meio a uma\r\nrajada de neve! Ou\u00E7a meu\r\nconselho e fique longe daquilo!",
        "Target": "Mate um Kushala Daora",
        "Fail": "A recompensa chega a 0\r\nou o tempo expira"
      },
      {
        "Language": "KOR",
        "Name": "\uC601\uD558\uC758 \uC9C0\uBC30\uC790",
        "Client": "\uB3C4\uB9DD\uCCD0 \uC628 \uB9C8\uC744 \uC8FC\uBBFC",
        "Description": "\uB09C \uB611\uB611\uD788 \uBD24\uC5B4. \uC2DC\uC57C\uB97C\r\n\uAC00\uB9AC\uB294 \uB208\uBCF4\uB77C \uD55C\uAC00\uC6B4\uB370\uC11C\r\n\uCDA4\uCD94\uB294 \uAC80\uC740 \uB0A0\uAC1C\uB97C! \uADF8\uAC74\r\n\uC778\uAC04\uC774 \uAC10\uB2F9\uD560 \uC218 \uC788\uB294 \uC874\uC7AC\uAC00\r\n\uC544\uB2C8\uC57C. \uC808\uB300 \uAC00\uC120 \uC548 \uB3FC! ",
